videos.description: UNC DB Malik Carney rips the ball from Georgia Tech RB Jerry Howard, gobbles up the fumble himself and trots 20 yards to the house.
videos.headline: UNC cashes in on rumble-6

videos.description: Georgia Tech RB Nathan Cottrell takes a reverse and sprints into the end zone untouched for an 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech knots the score with 11-yard TD
